  - Title: Srimad Bhagavatam
    Location: XI iii
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Renunciation-Detachment=Interiorization and Transmutation
    of the Faculties
  - 99
---
When one sees this universe as ephemeral, one gains true discrimination and
turns away from worldliness. The Self becomes the Saviour of self.
